{
  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "dialogic_010",
      "character": "",
      "text": "[He is sitting. Has been sitting so long that the ground seems shaped to him. He doesn't acknowledge you for a long moment.]"
    },
    {
      "event_id": "dialogic_010",
      "character": "The Buddhist",
      "text": "Sit."
    },
    {
      "event_id": "dialogic_020",
      "choices": [
        {"text": "[Sit down]", "condition": "", "destination": "choice_sit"},
        {"text": "I'm not here to meditate.", "condition": "", "destination": "choice_refuse"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "event_id": "dialogic_010",
      "label": "choice_refuse",
      "character": "The Buddhist",
      "text": "Then come back when you are."
    },
    {
      "event_id": "dialogic_010",
      "character": "",
      "text": "[He goes quiet. Completely quiet. The silence is not uncomfortable. That's what's uncomfortable.]"
    },
    {
      "event_id": "dialogic_000",
      "signal_name": "end_refuse"
    },
    {
      "event_id": "dialogic_010",
      "label": "choice_sit",
      "character": "",
      "text": "[You sit. The quiet expands around you both.]"
    },
    {
      "event_id": "dialogic_010",
      "character": "The Buddhist",
      "text": "You are attached to the idea that suffering should not exist."
    },
    {
      "event_id": "dialogic_010",
      "character": "The Buddhist",
      "text": "That attachment is suffering."
    },
    {
      "event_id": "dialogic_020",
      "choices": [
        {"text": "That's circular.", "condition": "", "destination": "sit_circular"},
        {"text": "You're saying I should just accept it.", "condition": "", "destination": "sit_accept"},
        {"text": "[Say nothing]", "condition": "", "destination": "sit_silence"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "event_id": "dialogic_010",
      "label": "sit_circular",
      "character": "The Buddhist",
      "text": "Yes. That's the point."
    },
    {
      "event_id": "dialogic_010",
      "character": "The Buddhist",
      "text": "The circle is the problem. You have been running its edge your entire life."
    },
    {
      "event_id": "dialogic_000",
      "signal_name": "add_compassion_1"
    },
    {
      "event_id": "dialogic_010",
      "label": "sit_accept",
      "character": "The Buddhist",
      "text": "I am saying you should observe it. Without needing it to be different."
    },
    {
      "event_id": "dialogic_010",
      "character": "The Buddhist",
      "text": "You cannot solve pain by hating it more efficiently."
    },
    {
      "event_id": "dialogic_000",
      "signal_name": "add_compassion_1"
    },
    {
      "event_id": "dialogic_010",
      "label": "sit_silence",
      "character": "",
      "text": "[You say nothing. He says nothing. Time passes. Something in your chest loosens — slightly, against your will.]"
    },
    {
      "event_id": "dialogic_010",
      "character": "The Buddhist",
      "text": "There."
    },
    {
      "event_id": "dialogic_000",
      "signal_name": "add_compassion_1"
    }
  ]
}
